*** Assistive Media
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       e4aef5a4-2b29-4747-906d-e78a199a1fdf
:END:
+ is a nonprofit service designed to help people who have _visual and reading impairments_.
+ A database of audio recordings is used to read to the user.
